text: Fryda Maria Wolff (born May 25, 1982) is an American voice actress. At a young age, Fryda Wolff attended Las Vegas Academy of the Arts high school during the same era as Matthew Gray Gubler, Rutina Wesley, Baron Vaughn and Ne-Yo. Fryda and Baron have been close friends since their freshman year of high school. She voice acts for many shows, movies and games. One of her most famous roles is The Collector from The Owl House, she is also the voice of DJ Suki and Satin & Chenille in Trolls: The Beat Goes On! and Trolls: TrollsTopia. ==Other websites== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:People from Las Vegas Category:American voice actors
